H0.text: leader of carthage in the first punic war. Hanno the Great

H1.text: leader of carthage in the first punic war. Hamilcar Barca

H2.text: leader of carthage in the first punic war. Hasdrubal the Fair

H3.text: leader of carthage in the first punic war. Xanthippus

A4.text: Hanno the Great may refer to any of three different leaders of ancient Carthage

A5.text: Hanno II and Hanno III are called megas in Greek in the histories of Appian and Zonaras

A6.text: Hamilcar is thought to be the best commander of the First Punic War.

A7.text: Hamilcar Barca was elected to sole command.
